{"tid":306041,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"救撚命 部野成日自房reboot","createTime":"2017-07-02T07:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T16:48:20.000Z","uid":75767,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd1247789892114aafa42dafa0df9fbd81825da","tid":306041,"uid":75767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:55:30.000Z","msg":"部野3年左右<br />\n大約兩個月前出事係畫面停左 要手動熄機再開<br />\n原來display card有事  佢地話寄返台灣 <br />\n寄返返嚟 香港 佢地俾過塊全新我 <br />\n咁用到最近又嚟料<br />\n<br />\n今次唔知死咩 自動reboot<br />\n有時一login入desktop就即刻自己重開<br />\n有時咩都唔做 冇開野係desktop又重開<br />\n有時一開某啲 soft就重開 <br />\n<br />\n以為火牛 ram 有事 已經換過新 (保養期)<br />\ndisplay card我抆左出嚟試 都有事<br />\nhd抆左出嚟都係咁<br />\nsdd window又重裝左 清左機 應該唔關毒事<br />\n<br />\n剩返cpu同板 我拎去俾佢地試<br />\n前者冇事 後者話cpu散熱膠入左cpu糟佢地自己搞唔到要寄台灣 咁琴日寄返返嚟 話搞惦左<br />\n咁我自己再買啲膏茶落cpu<br />\n返屋企搞左晚 又重裝過 玩左成晚又真係冇事 <br />\n屌佢老味啱啱又嚟料 一登入又重開<br />\n有時登入到用一陣又重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴打救下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15491359a6a02dc67063fc68000bdfffff5f79a9","tid":306041,"uid":75767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:57:22.000Z","msg":"有時好彩可以入到去<br />\n一開 chrome就 reboot"},{"pid":"58d2529b20f95113869040c4fe62d7eee799a4b2","tid":306041,"uid":71665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:03:31.000Z","msg":"換電腦啦"},{"pid":"a4768a80be0b38a8272f1b62de83977717100141","tid":306041,"uid":75767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"spec<br />\n牛 - cm gx 550w<br />\nram - crucial 8GB ddr3<br />\n板 - h97 d3h<br />\ndisplay - gtx770<br />\nplextor 128GB sdd"},{"pid":"6ba3881ee19e843f46f2356aa7270fd638ae89cb","tid":306041,"uid":75767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換電腦啦</blockquote><br />\n窮呀"},{"pid":"961ba118457a67b1bdded6c01ba2c56bca5786d8","tid":306041,"uid":2882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":